					"*テキスト*",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			en = {
				{
					name = {"文乃", "Fumino"},
					"“B-But... I’d never experienced any of my cooking remaining unfinished, so... Yes, my heart felt so disquieted... Indubitably...!”",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			cn = {
				{
					name = {"文乃"},
					"“但、但是……文乃没经历过自己做的料理被剩下的经验……所以，心里面乱哄哄的……滴咕滴咕滴咕……！”",
